# Docker Compose Dev Parity

- Infra-facing changes must be runnable through `docker compose` workflows.
- Keep service env vars consistent between local scripts and compose services.
- Update compose helper scripts and docs when service ports, commands, or dependencies change.
- Prefer deterministic startup via health checks and explicit service dependencies.
